{"content":"---\ntitle: \"'Exit Select' can only appear inside a 'Select' statement\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"vbc30099\"\n  - \"bc30099\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"BC30099\"\nms.assetid: 37c65fc8-6ad9-456a-80b8-66288c62ef24\n---\n# 'Exit Select' can only appear inside a 'Select' statement\nAn `Exit Select` statement occurs outside a `Select` block. `Exit Select` is valid only between a `Select` or `Select Case` statement and a corresponding `End Select` statement.  \n  \n **Error ID:** BC30099  \n  \n## To correct this error  \n  \n1.  Make sure a valid `Select` or `Select Case` statement precedes the `Exit Select` and a valid `End Select` statement appears after it.  \n  \n2.  Verify that other control structures within the `Select` block are correctly terminated.  \n  \n## See also\n\n- [Select...Case Statement](../../visual-basic/language-reference/statements/select-case-statement.md)\n","nodes":[{"pos":[4,218],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"title: \"'Exit Select' can only appear inside a 'Select' statement\"\nms.date: 07/20/2015\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"vbc30099\"\n  - \"bc30099\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"BC30099\"\nms.assetid: 37c65fc8-6ad9-456a-80b8-66288c62ef24","nodes":[{"content":"'Exit Select' can only appear inside a 'Select' statement","nodes":[{"pos":[0,57],"content":"'Exit Select' can only appear inside a 'Select' statement","nodes":[{"content":"'Exit Select' can only appear inside a 'Select' statement","pos":[0,57]}]}],"path":["title"],"nosxs":false}],"yml":true},{"pos":[225,282],"content":"'Exit Select' can only appear inside a 'Select' statement","linkify":"'Exit Select' can only appear inside a 'Select' statement","nodes":[{"content":"'Exit Select' can only appear inside a 'Select' statement","pos":[0,57]}]},{"content":"An <ph id=\"ph1\">`Exit Select`</ph> statement occurs outside a <ph id=\"ph2\">`Select`</ph> block.","pos":[283,342],"source":"An `Exit Select` statement occurs outside a `Select` block."},{"